Background Information:


Sand Grove Capital Management LLP »
Sand Grove Capital Management LLP is a British private company located in London, with subsidiaries in Cayman Islands, that provides investment advice. It was founded in 2014 by Simon Alfred Noel Davies, he has been the CEO since the inception date.




In The News:




                            Sand Grove Capital Management LLP disclosed in a filing on March 31, 2017 that it increased its stake in Time Warner, Inc.                            


                            June 15, 2017  •  RelSci                        





                            Sand Grove Capital Management LLP disclosed a new stake in Syneron Medical Ltd. in a filing on May 10, 2017                            


                            May 17, 2017  •  RelSci                        





                            Sand Grove Capital Management LLP disclosed in a filing on March 31, 2017 that it reduced its stake in Rite Aid Corp.                            


                            May 17, 2017  •  RelSci                        









